  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities<br /></p><p>Assist in manpower the planning for weekly duty roster<br /></p><p>Plan modular trainings for new hires and existing staff<br /></p><p>Monitor any renovation projects for rooms<br /></p><p>Assist Manager in preparing monthly updates report to the Management</p><p>Overall in charge in handling resolving issues with customers complaints.<br /></p><p>Reach out to customers on service promotion.<br /></p><p>Responding to customer enquiriers.<br /></p><p>Keeping records interactions,transactions,comments and feedback from customers to improve services.<br /></p><p>Supervise and manage service staff in serving customers in a friendly and helpful manner.<br /></p><p>Ensure customer satisfaction and provide customer support.<br /></p><p>Create welcome team to great customers lead them to their seats.<br /></p><p>Lead and manage team in achieving KPIs on sales and operational targets<br /></p><p>Assist Manager in monitoring and ensuring smooth execution of promotions and marketing campaign through strong internal collaboration with Marketing department in order to drive sales revenue</p>",
